# trusted_paths
# =============
# Trusted sources do not automatically bypass every rule.  The exact bypasses
# are controlled by trusted_bypass_* options in cleanfeed.local.
#
# Exact Path token:
# (?:^|!)trusted-transit\.example(?:!|$)
#
# Any one of three trusted feeds:
# (?:^|!)(?:feed1|feed2|feed3)\.example\.net(?:!|$)
#
# Keep boundaries.  A bare hostname fragment may trust unrelated paths.
